# 📝 Lunar Planner

A simple and interactive to-do list web application where users can **add, organize, and manage tasks** with priority levels, deadlines, and categories. The app features **drag-and-drop reordering**, task filtering, and **local storage** support to keep tasks saved between sessions.

## 🌟 Features

✅ **Add Tasks** – Create tasks with a title, priority (Low, Medium, High), category, and due date.  
✅ **Drag & Drop Reordering** – Easily rearrange tasks by dragging them.  
✅ **Mark Tasks as Complete** – Check off completed tasks and filter them out.  
✅ **Filter Tasks** – View tasks based on priority, category, or due date.  
✅ **Persistent Storage** – Tasks are saved in **local storage**, so they remain even after refreshing the page.  

